K9 Rover in Granite Quarry                    Testing was            c onducted at Graniterock's            A.R. Wilson Quarry Site in Aromas, Calif.               Scientists chose the quarry site for the field experiment and            to test its autonomous operational capabilities in a remote, non-vegetated            location.    Graniterock offered            its 100-year-old quarry operation to NASA after Graniterock learned            that the space agency was looking for a site to test the rover. First Ice, Last Ice, and Ice Duration                  Documentation: First Ice, Last Ice,          and Ice Duration  [pdf]          The GRID (ASCII files) and PLOT (PNG image files) files contain the          results of an analysis of ice cover grids for dates of first ice, last          ice and ice duration (total number of days with ice cover) for each winter          season from 1973 to 2002, and for statistics (average, minimum and maximum)          across all 30 winter seasons. These data have been compiled for dates          when ice concentration was first and last reported to be equal or greater          than nine threshold values: 10%, 20%, 30%, 40%, 50%, 60%, 70%, 80% and          90%.          These data are based on observed ice concentrations from the grid ice          concentration data set described in Assel et al (2002). Details of the                  analysis procedures and observations on trends in these data will be         published in a forthcoming report.          File name definitions for          the uncompressed files, data codes for first ice, last ice and ice duration          and file formats for the GRID files are given in the documentation. PGE21 v2.2.29 test completed 02/11/2001     Purpose  LSST group has completed the test for PGE21 v2.2.29 MOD09A1 L3 Land Surface Reflectance Loader MDL10.  This 8-day (data days 241-256 year 2000) test is mainly testing for changes to the compositing of 500m data, especially to eliminate cloud shadows and to select for pixels at a low view angle.  The detailed   history of this PGE  is available.   Input data  The input data (L1A, L1B, L2, and  L2G) are from the previous test, in November 2000, data days 241-256 year 2000.  The previous test PGEs and versions can be found on  November 2000 report .  Output Data  1) The ESDT outputs from this test are located on UNIX mo1 at /MODLAND/ftp/LSST-Jan2001/MOD09A1 directory.  2) The MOD09A1 directory contains 2000241, 2000249, and logfiles directories.  3) The 2000241 and 2000249 directories contain MOD09A1's hdf file, MOD09A1's dump file, and a comparison file of PGE21 between v2.2.29 and v2.2.24.  The current output MOD09A1 of this test has been used to compare with the previous output MOD09A1 (PGE21 v2.2.24, LSST-Nov2000 test).  The hdf's comparison files are located at  LSST-Nov2000/MOD09A1/2000241/   and  LSST-Nov2000/MOD09A1/2000249/ .  4) The logfiles directory contains log files of this test.  The output directories (Test data output files listing) are listed below.     To access the data  There are two ways to access the above directories:  1) via the www:  ftp://mo1.nascom.nasa.gov:9000/LSST-Jan2001/MOD09A1/   2) the UNIX:  %ftp mo1.nascom.nasa.gov 9000  login name anonymous  %cd LSST-Jan2001/MOD09A1      Test data output files listing   LSST-Jan2001/MOD09A1:  2000241/ 2000249/ logfiles/   2000241:   MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.001.2001042223700.hdf  compare_MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.001  dump_MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.001.2001042223700.hdf  2000249:   MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.001.2001042230101.hdf  compare_MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.001  dump_MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.001.2001042230101.hdf   logfiles:  A2000241/L2G-3/h10v05/   and      A2000249/L2G-3/h10v05:   MDL10_1_MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.002.hdf.log  MDL10_2_MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.002.hdf.log  MODLM_QA.MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.001.2001042223700.hdf.log  MODLM_QA.MOD09A1.A2000241.h10v05.001.2001042223700.hdf.log.met  PGE21.A2000241.h10v05.pid434814.LogReport  PGE21.A2000241.h10v05.pid434814.LogStatus  PGE21.A2000241.h10v05.pid434814.LogUser  PGE21.A2000241.h10v05.pid434814.pcf  MDL10_1_MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.002.hdf.log  MDL10_2_MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.002.hdf.log  MODLM_QA.MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.001.2001042230101.hdf.log  MODLM_QA.MOD09A1.A2000249.h10v05.001.2001042230101.hdf.log.met  PGE21.A2000249.h10v05.pid435305.LogReport  PGE21.A2000249.h10v05.pid435305.LogStatus  PGE21.A2000249.h10v05.pid435305.LogUser  PGE21.A2000249.h10v05.pid435305.pcf     To MODIS LSSPT Home Page        Created 23 February 2001 (wd)
